overview: Comedian Chris Parker presents this part stand-up, part documentary, one-of-a-kind special! He travels to Christchurch and the place he discovered his passion for making people laugh - his high school.
tagline: Comedian Chris Parker returns to the battleground of his adolescence, Christchurch Boys' High School, to share some laughs and shine a spotlight on all-male education in today's society.
title: Chris Parker: Back To School
